3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a deep learning-based approach for road extraction, which falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The proposed approach uses residual units, which are a type of neural network architecture.
